maildrop-log-colorize.rb README
===============================

Overview
--------

Maildrop log colorizer.

Usage
-----

The usual:

    $ tail -f path/to/maildrop.log | maildrop-logcolorize.rb

  or

    $ maildrop-log-colorize.rb path/to/maildrop.log

See Maildrop::LogColorize::CONFIG for color settings.

